[And we "fight" about mask mandates... Guilty parties include not just the sales people of these counterfeit documents but also the individuals purchasing them. It is nice to read there have been custodial penalties in the countries where this has been uncovered. Given the requirement of a number of states in the USA that have mandatory 14-day quarantine when traveling from a high risk state, but can be shortened if there is proof of negative test following 3-4 days after arrival, one suspects this will become a lucrative business in the USA as well. A very sad state of affairs. - Mod.MPP]

